WEBVTT

01:43.009 --> 01:45.990
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.100 --> 01:48.940
[Episode 24]

01:49.870 --> 01:50.729
Coach Zhou,

01:50.830 --> 01:52.140
you're out for a walk again?

01:52.160 --> 01:52.860
Yeah.

01:52.880 --> 01:53.750
Coach Zhou,

01:53.950 --> 01:56.009
you're so good to your wife.

01:56.030 --> 01:57.770
It's been almost 20 years.

01:58.030 --> 01:58.430
Yeah.

01:58.509 --> 01:58.990
Goodbye.

01:59.009 --> 01:59.509
Goodbye.

02:06.350 --> 02:07.340
Coach Zhou.

02:08.639 --> 02:09.630
What brings you here?

02:10.389 --> 02:11.550
Well,

02:11.870 --> 02:13.580
there's something I want to ask you.

02:16.200 --> 02:17.130
What is it?

02:17.950 --> 02:19.390
How about we talk inside?

02:20.950 --> 02:21.470
Alright.

02:21.790 --> 02:22.340
Let's go.

02:45.610 --> 02:46.630
Call me if you need anything.

02:52.110 --> 02:52.990
Take a seat.

02:54.390 --> 02:55.200
Coach Zhou,

02:55.550 --> 02:56.460
how have you been?

02:58.670 --> 02:59.350
Same as always.

03:02.910 --> 03:04.720
It's been hard for you these years.

03:05.070 --> 03:06.070
I've gotten used to it.

03:07.590 --> 03:08.520
What about you?

03:08.710 --> 03:09.850
You came all the way here.

03:10.190 --> 03:11.000
What's the matter?

03:13.080 --> 03:15.030
I want to ask you about something.

03:16.470 --> 03:17.400
Back in school,

03:17.430 --> 03:20.240
there was a girl named Ding Jing.

03:20.670 --> 03:21.390
Do you remember her?

03:23.990 --> 03:24.710
Kind of.

03:28.190 --> 03:29.750
She was killed not too long ago.

03:33.790 --> 03:34.550
I've heard about it.

03:37.950 --> 03:38.640
Coach Zhou,

03:39.870 --> 03:41.050
did you still have contact

03:41.110 --> 03:41.870
with Ding Jing?

03:44.230 --> 03:45.030
No.

03:46.829 --> 03:47.850
I had no reason

03:48.230 --> 03:49.510
to stay in touch with her.

03:52.190 --> 03:52.990
Since when did you

03:53.030 --> 03:53.990
stop contacting her?

03:54.230 --> 03:56.350
We never really had any contact.

03:59.270 --> 04:00.510
Here's the thing.

04:01.710 --> 04:04.320
When Ding Jing was at school,

04:04.470 --> 04:05.760
as you may know,

04:05.870 --> 04:07.440
she was pretty arrogant and domineering.

04:08.590 --> 04:09.510
At that time,

04:09.670 --> 04:11.530
she bullied a girl in her class

04:13.030 --> 04:13.950
named Deng Man.

04:15.280 --> 04:16.089
Do you remember that?

04:32.790 --> 04:34.010
It's been too long.

04:35.680 --> 04:36.840
I can't really recall.

04:39.590 --> 04:41.200
Yeah, it has been so many years.

04:44.830 --> 04:45.760
Coach Zhou.

04:45.909 --> 04:46.710
Deng Man

04:48.070 --> 04:49.430
confessed to me back in school.

04:49.450 --> 04:50.930
You were the one who mentioned that, right?

04:55.909 --> 04:57.110
Ever since I got sick,

04:57.130 --> 04:57.900
well,

04:58.680 --> 05:00.230
my memory

05:00.710 --> 05:02.570
has been really spotty.

05:02.670 --> 05:03.630
Some things I remember,

05:03.670 --> 05:04.690
some I don't.

05:05.950 --> 05:07.020
You came all this way,

05:07.050 --> 05:09.200
and you're asking these questions because…

05:09.630 --> 05:10.480
Sorry, I went off-topic.

05:10.990 --> 05:12.760
Actually, I just want to know more

05:12.860 --> 05:13.930
about Ding Jing.

05:14.430 --> 05:15.800
Coach Zhou, let me be honest with you.

05:15.830 --> 05:16.610
Actually,

05:16.910 --> 05:17.590
we found during our investigation

05:17.630 --> 05:19.060
that before Ding Jing was killed,

05:19.110 --> 05:20.330
she actually

05:20.430 --> 05:21.310
had contact with you.

05:23.710 --> 05:24.310
I'm not

05:24.950 --> 05:26.510
implying anything, Coach Zhou.

05:26.830 --> 05:27.870
I just want to know

05:28.390 --> 05:30.650
what you two talked about,

05:30.880 --> 05:32.159
the specifics of it.

05:33.350 --> 05:34.920
I want to see if it might

05:35.990 --> 05:37.070
help us solve the case.

05:55.790 --> 05:57.050
I'm really sorry,

05:57.909 --> 05:59.690
but my wife isn't doing well.

05:59.720 --> 06:01.540
No matter what it is, could we…

06:02.040 --> 06:03.110
could we discuss it another time?

06:03.310 --> 06:03.830
No problem.

06:06.350 --> 06:07.120
Coach Zhou.

06:10.030 --> 06:11.480
If you have any difficulties

06:11.710 --> 06:12.930
or need any help,

06:13.390 --> 06:14.030
feel free to contact me.

07:01.790 --> 07:02.460
Thank you.

07:13.500 --> 07:14.310
That's

07:14.390 --> 07:16.090
Yu Bofeng's rumored girlfriend?

07:16.600 --> 07:17.290
Right.

07:17.510 --> 07:18.720
Can you believe…

07:23.810 --> 07:24.710
She's so much older

07:24.710 --> 07:26.220
than Yu Bofeng.

07:26.350 --> 07:27.460
Way too old.

07:28.110 --> 07:29.110
Is it really her?

07:29.270 --> 07:29.630
Yes.

07:29.750 --> 07:31.070
She's quite good-looking, isn't she?

07:34.350 --> 07:44.100
[Ninghai Police Academy]

07:37.670 --> 07:38.150
Come in.

07:41.230 --> 07:42.180
Hello, Professor Yu.

07:42.350 --> 07:43.190
We're from Yu Bofeng's

07:43.190 --> 07:43.950
PR team.

07:45.630 --> 07:46.110
Hello.

07:46.190 --> 07:47.110
Please, have a seat.

07:47.790 --> 07:48.420
No need.

07:48.790 --> 07:49.710
We're here today to

07:49.710 --> 07:50.870
address the issue of you and Yu Bofeng

07:50.870 --> 07:51.920
being secretly photographed.

07:53.470 --> 07:54.280
Secretly photographed?

07:55.750 --> 07:56.830
Our team has been working

07:56.830 --> 07:57.470
to suppress the rumors online

07:57.470 --> 07:58.350
over the past two days.

07:58.980 --> 07:59.830
By now, Yu Bofeng

07:59.830 --> 08:00.940
has already lost

08:01.070 --> 08:02.110
two business deals

08:02.110 --> 08:02.780
because of the scandal with you,

08:03.270 --> 08:04.390
and other business activities

08:04.430 --> 08:05.800
are on hold too.

08:07.190 --> 08:07.820
So,

08:08.750 --> 08:10.270
what does this have to do with me?

08:12.070 --> 08:13.590
As Yu Bofeng's teacher,

08:13.670 --> 08:15.110
I'm sure you don't want to see

08:15.150 --> 08:16.070
his career thrown into chaos

08:16.070 --> 08:17.080
just because you two

08:17.110 --> 08:18.630
ate noodles together, right?

08:21.790 --> 08:22.630
So?

08:23.510 --> 08:25.080
So we hope

08:25.120 --> 08:25.830
you can work with us

08:25.830 --> 08:26.800
to record a video,

08:26.870 --> 08:28.140
a clarification video,

08:28.230 --> 08:29.070
to clarify that

08:29.070 --> 08:29.710
you're just

08:29.750 --> 08:31.100
teacher and student,

08:31.230 --> 08:32.270
and that privately,

08:32.270 --> 08:33.669
you won't have any further contact.

08:38.950 --> 08:40.429
A clarification video?

08:40.330 --> 08:44.490
[Ninghai Police Academy]

08:40.460 --> 08:41.110
Yes.

08:45.870 --> 08:46.950
Firstly,

08:47.070 --> 08:48.170
I'm just Yu Bofeng's

08:48.270 --> 08:49.960
teacher.

08:50.070 --> 08:50.660
Secondly,

08:51.470 --> 08:52.740
it's absurd that Yu Bofeng's future

08:52.740 --> 08:53.470
will be ruined

08:53.510 --> 08:54.550
by a rumor

08:54.550 --> 08:55.510
that's completely not true.

08:56.070 --> 08:57.350
We understand all that,

08:57.350 --> 08:58.140
but

08:58.270 --> 08:59.140
it won't convince his fans

08:59.140 --> 09:00.110
or business partners.

09:00.470 --> 09:01.330
Thirdly,

09:02.030 --> 09:03.580
I've done nothing wrong,

09:03.940 --> 09:04.950
and I'm not obligated

09:04.990 --> 09:06.070
to convince anyone.

09:09.680 --> 09:10.430
Professor Yu,

09:10.830 --> 09:11.430
if you

09:11.470 --> 09:13.000
have any requests,

09:13.070 --> 09:14.270
you can just let us know.

09:14.350 --> 09:14.900
It's alright.

09:15.510 --> 09:15.990
What kind of requests

09:15.990 --> 09:17.070
should I have?

09:19.180 --> 09:20.220
It's simple.

09:20.550 --> 09:22.030
We won't let you record the video for free.

09:22.310 --> 09:23.360
Name your price,

09:23.440 --> 09:24.940
and we'll do our best to meet it.

09:24.970 --> 09:26.170
That's what we mean.

09:31.710 --> 09:33.190
Is this Mr. Wen's idea?

09:35.360 --> 09:37.070
So Zhou Zhicheng

09:37.150 --> 09:40.320
deliberately made Dr. Lu think

09:40.380 --> 09:45.230
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

09:40.590 --> 09:42.340
that Deng Man confessed to you,

09:43.500 --> 09:45.220
and he didn't deny knowing Ding Jing.

09:45.790 --> 09:47.330
The way he talks…

09:48.460 --> 09:49.440
It's strange.

09:49.630 --> 09:50.800
My gut feeling is

09:51.550 --> 09:52.750
he's hiding something,

09:52.770 --> 09:55.430
but he won't tell me.

09:56.690 --> 09:57.350
So, Captain Jiang,

09:57.390 --> 09:58.070
you think the two of them

09:58.110 --> 09:58.870
were in cahoots?

09:59.860 --> 10:01.400
I wouldn't jump to conclusions.

10:08.310 --> 10:08.870
Hello?

10:09.230 --> 10:10.250
Hey, Jiang Chengyi.

10:11.550 --> 10:12.850
I just found out

10:12.900 --> 10:15.560
that Zhou Zhicheng was diagnosed with cancer three years ago.

10:15.710 --> 10:16.310
He's been undergoing

10:16.310 --> 10:17.400
chemotherapy with imported medication

10:17.470 --> 10:18.440
all these years.

10:18.510 --> 10:20.340
He's spent almost a million yuan on it.

10:20.480 --> 10:21.300
Really?

10:21.630 --> 10:23.030
But do you remember

10:23.150 --> 10:24.440
his family was very poor

10:24.480 --> 10:25.910
when we were in college?

10:26.140 --> 10:28.420
His wife's been bedridden for years.

10:28.660 --> 10:30.280
We even donated money to him.

10:30.670 --> 10:31.230
Yeah, yeah,

10:31.310 --> 10:32.270
I remember that.

10:34.470 --> 10:35.220
So I think

10:35.270 --> 10:36.570
there's more to this.

10:37.470 --> 10:37.870
How about this?

10:37.870 --> 10:38.790
I'll send you the screenshots.

10:39.270 --> 10:39.990
Take a look

10:40.030 --> 10:41.150
and see if they help.

10:41.400 --> 10:41.850
Alright.

10:42.430 --> 10:43.160
Send them over.

10:44.000 --> 10:44.860
Okay, I'll hang up now.

10:49.910 --> 10:54.640
[Have Film, Have Fun]

10:53.270 --> 10:54.200
I understand your concerns.

10:54.230 --> 10:54.750
Yes.

10:55.550 --> 10:56.030
Alright.

10:56.110 --> 10:57.070
Give me a bit more time

10:57.110 --> 10:57.910
to make this…

11:02.840 --> 11:03.470
Um…

11:03.470 --> 11:04.360
I'll get back to you later.

11:08.340 --> 11:09.470
What is it, Professor Yu?

11:10.750 --> 11:11.870
Is this your idea, Mr. Wen?

11:16.750 --> 11:18.110
PR companies are just like this.

11:18.160 --> 11:19.470
They want to resolve problems quickly,

11:19.510 --> 11:19.960
so…

11:19.990 --> 11:21.230
So you think

11:21.630 --> 11:22.430
money

11:22.510 --> 11:23.550
is a quick solution

11:23.550 --> 11:24.360
to all problems,

11:25.270 --> 11:26.000
right?

11:26.590 --> 11:28.110
I have to consider everyone.

11:31.790 --> 11:32.640
This industry

11:32.670 --> 11:33.550
is a game of fame and fortune.

11:33.910 --> 11:34.670
I can't trust

11:34.670 --> 11:35.430
anyone's promises.

11:35.470 --> 11:36.710
I can only trust the law.

11:40.060 --> 11:41.640
Precisely because I respect everyone,

11:42.180 --> 11:42.760
I need to ensure

11:42.790 --> 11:44.120
everyone's interests are protected.

11:46.550 --> 11:47.360
I still have things to do.

11:47.390 --> 11:48.860
Professor Yu, if there's anything,

11:48.960 --> 11:49.790
you can call me.

11:49.810 --> 11:50.610
Mr. Wen.

11:52.620 --> 11:54.290
I recall you mentioned

11:54.460 --> 11:56.520
you took psychology as an elective

11:56.540 --> 11:57.150
in college, right?

12:03.620 --> 12:04.260
Yes.

12:04.790 --> 12:06.120
Then you should know

12:06.270 --> 12:06.990
everyone has

12:07.030 --> 12:08.410
their own individuality

12:08.750 --> 12:09.440
and the right

12:09.470 --> 12:10.670
to choose their own fate.

12:11.440 --> 12:13.300
Yu Bofeng has the right to decide

12:13.400 --> 12:14.520
whether to meet me or not.

12:16.800 --> 12:17.990
You don't have the authority

12:17.990 --> 12:19.110
to decide whether I can see him or not.

12:20.430 --> 12:22.420
From what I know of Yu Bofeng,

12:22.790 --> 12:23.990
he's not someone

12:24.020 --> 12:25.510
who can be easily swayed by profit.

12:26.840 --> 12:27.660
So everything

12:27.660 --> 12:29.200
you're doing today

12:29.950 --> 12:31.290
is solely for yourself.

12:32.410 --> 12:34.080
I'm running such a big company.

12:34.150 --> 12:35.620
If it's not for the company's interests,

12:35.910 --> 12:36.830
then what's it for?

12:37.710 --> 12:38.510
For you?

12:44.000 --> 12:46.120
Actually, compared to Yu Bofeng,

12:46.470 --> 12:47.910
I'm more interested in you.

12:50.380 --> 12:51.060
Is that so?

12:54.310 --> 12:55.230
You possess

12:55.230 --> 12:56.270
all the traits

12:56.270 --> 12:57.380
of a high-IQ criminal—

12:58.740 --> 12:59.950
exceptional intelligence,

12:59.990 --> 13:01.150
meticulous planning,

13:01.950 --> 13:03.120
and rebellious views.

13:03.910 --> 13:05.470
Most importantly,

13:06.390 --> 13:07.670
you were connected to

13:07.960 --> 13:09.140
Deng Man,

13:09.440 --> 13:10.230
Wang Qianqian,

13:11.390 --> 13:12.270
and Ding Jing.

13:14.910 --> 13:16.190
I only knew them.

13:17.310 --> 13:18.200
This is not something

13:18.230 --> 13:19.310
you can joke about.

13:20.000 --> 13:21.180
I'm not joking.

13:24.920 --> 13:25.730
Professor Yu,

13:26.030 --> 13:27.140
as I've said before,

13:27.190 --> 13:28.470
we businesspeople

13:28.470 --> 13:29.780
hate trouble the most.

13:31.040 --> 13:32.330
Is there anything else?

13:36.650 --> 13:38.010
Well, I'm sorry to say,

13:38.670 --> 13:39.710
but life always

13:39.810 --> 13:41.420
comes with plenty of trouble.

14:07.430 --> 14:08.470
Been waiting a while?

14:08.980 --> 14:09.640
It's fine.

14:09.760 --> 14:10.770
You came together?

14:10.830 --> 14:11.230
Yeah.

14:11.870 --> 14:12.660
Hello, Dr. Lu.

14:12.710 --> 14:13.570
I'm Yu Zheng.

14:13.750 --> 14:14.390
Hello.

14:14.470 --> 14:15.480
He told me about you.

14:15.510 --> 14:16.400
You're quite an expert

14:16.430 --> 14:17.790
in criminal psychology.

14:18.070 --> 14:19.070
Thank you for helping me look into

14:19.070 --> 14:20.050
Man's case.

14:22.190 --> 14:23.030
I've gone through

14:23.070 --> 14:23.790
the clues I have

14:23.790 --> 14:24.630
and made a mind map.

14:24.710 --> 14:25.670
Take a look.

14:27.020 --> 14:29.150
I've arranged the clues

14:29.170 --> 14:30.340
related to Deng Man

14:29.410 --> 14:31.260
[Deng Man] [Zhou Zhicheng] [Ding Jing]

14:30.370 --> 14:31.470
chronologically.

14:31.490 --> 14:32.880
They're "Hiroshima Mon Amour,"

14:33.230 --> 14:34.350
the unknown video,

14:34.510 --> 14:35.600
the alternate Weibo account,

14:35.710 --> 14:37.010
Deng Man's suicide note,

14:37.190 --> 14:37.870
and the anonymous letter

14:37.940 --> 14:39.070
from three years ago.

14:39.550 --> 14:40.910
Let's extract the key points

14:40.910 --> 14:42.280
from all the clues.

14:42.430 --> 14:43.230
"Hiroshima Mon Amour"

14:43.230 --> 14:44.650
symbolizes a forbidden love.

14:44.870 --> 14:45.820
The unknown video

14:45.910 --> 14:46.490
was Ding Jing's method

14:46.550 --> 14:47.980
of threatening Deng Man.

14:48.110 --> 14:49.000
The alternate Weibo account

14:49.110 --> 14:49.910
was Deng Man's

14:49.950 --> 14:51.400
accusation against Ding Jing.

14:51.710 --> 14:52.510
The suicide note

14:52.530 --> 14:53.720
explains the reason for her death.

14:54.080 --> 14:55.430
The anonymous letter from three years ago

14:55.510 --> 14:56.480
indicates someone

14:56.510 --> 14:57.750
was questioning the cause of Deng Man's death.

14:58.510 --> 14:59.880
The biggest problem now

14:59.910 --> 15:00.780
is that when we connect

15:00.870 --> 15:01.870
all the clues together,

15:02.110 --> 15:03.040
the logic doesn't hold,

15:03.190 --> 15:04.270
and they contradict each other.

15:06.550 --> 15:08.150
If the suicide note is real,

15:08.360 --> 15:09.060
then Deng Man

15:09.060 --> 15:10.880
took her own life because she couldn't have you.

15:11.350 --> 15:12.600
"Hiroshima Mon Amour"

15:12.630 --> 15:13.590
and that anonymous letter

15:13.590 --> 15:14.610
wouldn't make sense.

15:14.950 --> 15:15.830
But if the anonymous letter

15:15.830 --> 15:17.330
is genuine,

15:17.870 --> 15:18.950
then the suicide note

15:18.950 --> 15:19.820
is questionable,

15:20.350 --> 15:21.310
and there must be more

15:21.330 --> 15:22.580
to her cause of death.

15:24.760 --> 15:25.380
Oh, right,

15:25.470 --> 15:26.350
I've discovered

15:26.350 --> 15:27.030
a new clue recently.

15:28.230 --> 15:30.110
Over the eight years since Deng Man's death,

15:30.310 --> 15:31.310
Zhou Zhicheng

15:31.330 --> 15:33.140
visited her grave many times,

15:33.250 --> 15:35.350
fourteen in total.

15:36.230 --> 15:37.110
To me,

15:37.150 --> 15:38.000
that goes beyond

15:38.070 --> 15:39.550
a normal teacher-student relationship.

15:40.830 --> 15:42.430
So, are you saying

15:43.500 --> 15:46.350
there was something between Deng Man and Coach Zhou?

15:47.750 --> 15:48.720
Girls like Deng Man,

15:48.790 --> 15:50.190
who grow up unloved,

15:50.230 --> 15:51.380
often develop a tendency

15:51.630 --> 15:53.350
to seek father-like figures.

15:53.430 --> 15:53.960
It's actually

15:53.990 --> 15:55.290
quite common.

15:55.790 --> 15:57.190
So it's not entirely impossible

15:57.230 --> 15:58.670
that she was involved with Coach Zhou.

15:59.290 --> 16:00.390
Besides, doesn't "Hiroshima Mon Amour"

16:00.390 --> 16:01.770
perfectly align with

16:01.830 --> 16:02.470
the idea of being involved

16:02.470 --> 16:03.630
with a married man?

16:05.190 --> 16:06.630
So Coach Zhou lied to me.

16:06.710 --> 16:07.870
I asked him about this,

16:07.950 --> 16:09.490
and he said he wasn't close to Deng Man.

16:10.790 --> 16:12.580
These are just my theories,

16:12.750 --> 16:13.780
but I think the general direction

16:13.830 --> 16:15.150
is correct.

16:15.750 --> 16:17.030
As for evidence,

16:17.870 --> 16:19.350
Captain Jiang can find it.

16:19.950 --> 16:20.390
Alright.

16:22.230 --> 16:23.310
Do you have

16:23.710 --> 16:24.590
any updates on your side?

16:26.070 --> 16:27.100
There are some clues,

16:27.140 --> 16:29.280
but they're still incomplete.

16:29.310 --> 16:30.070
I'll let you know

16:30.110 --> 16:31.030
once I've confirmed them.

16:31.360 --> 16:31.750
Alright.

16:32.550 --> 16:33.280
Thanks for your help.

16:33.350 --> 16:33.830
No problem.

16:34.070 --> 16:34.470
I'll get going.

16:34.590 --> 16:34.990
Okay.

16:45.630 --> 16:46.910
I need to go find Coach Zhou.

16:49.740 --> 16:50.540
I'll go with you.

16:52.820 --> 16:54.770
Wouldn't it be inappropriate for you to go?

16:55.780 --> 16:56.520
No.

16:56.550 --> 16:58.550
For now, this is still a civil case.

16:58.590 --> 16:59.790
Besides, I'd worry

16:59.790 --> 17:00.590
if you went alone.

17:10.190 --> 17:10.880
Are you there?

17:11.440 --> 17:12.980
My phone was confiscated.

17:13.010 --> 17:14.109
I just borrowed someone else's phone

17:14.150 --> 17:15.160
to log into WeChat.

17:15.329 --> 17:16.480
How are you doing now?

17:16.710 --> 17:19.589
[Yu Bofeng] [Delete]

17:21.540 --> 17:22.010
[Yu Bofeng]

17:22.130 --> 17:23.319
[Settings] [Block]

17:43.110 --> 17:44.030
You still need

17:44.030 --> 17:44.890
to do the rehab.

17:45.790 --> 17:46.780
Maybe one day,

17:46.910 --> 17:47.990
you'll be able to stand up again.

17:58.160 --> 17:58.820
Alright.

18:00.230 --> 18:01.330
Time to eat.

18:02.270 --> 18:03.110
Time to eat.

18:07.140 --> 18:08.390
I just made some porridge.

18:08.420 --> 18:09.440
It's been sitting for a bit.

18:10.020 --> 18:10.710
I tried it.

18:10.710 --> 18:11.430
It's not hot anymore.

18:15.780 --> 18:16.230
Here.

18:17.870 --> 18:18.350
Come on.

18:24.680 --> 18:25.900
Still angry?

18:29.430 --> 18:30.780
I know I've made mistakes,

18:33.070 --> 18:34.380
but I've told you

18:35.700 --> 18:37.120
I'll never do it again.

18:37.750 --> 18:38.830
Forgive me, okay?

18:40.300 --> 18:42.110
Right now, you only have me,

18:42.570 --> 18:43.830
and I only have you.

18:45.030 --> 18:46.290
Let's spend the rest of our lives together.

18:56.430 --> 18:56.950
Here,

18:57.260 --> 18:57.960
have some porridge.

19:00.770 --> 19:01.430
Have some porridge.

19:09.200 --> 19:10.410
What do you want?

19:11.080 --> 19:12.620
I've apologized to you.

19:13.870 --> 19:15.540
I've promised I'll never do it again.

19:17.470 --> 19:19.160
You just won't forgive me.

19:20.860 --> 19:22.160
You're never satisfied.

19:22.230 --> 19:23.550
What do you want from me?

19:24.910 --> 19:26.770
What exactly do you want me to do?

19:38.450 --> 19:39.010
Come on.

19:39.680 --> 19:40.320
Eat.

19:41.150 --> 19:41.750
Come on.

19:42.510 --> 19:43.190
Open your mouth.

19:44.430 --> 19:45.030
Open your mouth.

19:45.750 --> 19:46.430
Eat.

19:46.780 --> 19:47.500
Do you hear me?

20:01.970 --> 20:03.280
You don't want to live anymore, do you?

20:05.780 --> 20:07.130
Then let's die together.

20:09.370 --> 20:11.470
After all, you've long given up on life!

20:11.790 --> 20:12.770
Fine.

20:13.520 --> 20:14.790
If you don't want to live, then don't!

20:14.830 --> 20:16.150
Let's just die together!

20:16.470 --> 20:17.630
Die together!

20:38.590 --> 20:40.230
I brought back some porridge from the cafeteria.

20:42.030 --> 20:43.500
Eat some, okay?

20:45.630 --> 20:46.110
Here.

20:51.800 --> 20:52.810
It's pumpkin porridge,

20:53.020 --> 20:54.030
a little sweet.

20:55.710 --> 20:56.710
Come on, try it.

21:03.010 --> 21:03.910
You haven't eaten anything

21:03.910 --> 21:04.670
for several days.

21:05.510 --> 21:06.710
You can't go on like this.

21:14.830 --> 21:15.420
Honey,

21:16.510 --> 21:17.590
I know you're devastated.

21:19.510 --> 21:21.160
You probably wish you were dead.

21:21.390 --> 21:22.990
If I could take your place,

21:24.610 --> 21:25.930
I absolutely would.

21:28.070 --> 21:29.320
Don't be afraid, okay?

21:31.440 --> 21:32.550
I won't abandon you.

21:35.080 --> 21:36.370
I'll stay with you,

21:38.070 --> 21:39.110
watch over you,

21:40.550 --> 21:41.470
and take care of you.

21:43.400 --> 21:45.030
I'll never leave you.

21:46.900 --> 21:47.990
Believe me, okay?

21:49.550 --> 21:50.590
I promise.

21:52.440 --> 21:53.230
I swear,

21:55.030 --> 21:56.500
I'll take care of you forever.

21:59.250 --> 22:00.150
Coach Zhou,

22:00.540 --> 22:02.620
you deserve the title

22:02.870 --> 22:04.000
of Moral Model of Ninghai.

22:05.800 --> 22:07.050
Thank you, Principal.

22:10.790 --> 22:11.770
Dear audience,

22:11.810 --> 22:12.520
sitting next to me now

22:12.550 --> 22:13.890
is Mr. Zhou Zhicheng,

22:13.950 --> 22:14.830
an exceptional coach

22:14.870 --> 22:16.090
who has tirelessly looked after

22:16.150 --> 22:18.160
his paralyzed wife

22:18.280 --> 22:19.690
for nearly five years.

22:19.830 --> 22:20.870
Coach Zhou Zhicheng,

22:20.890 --> 22:22.020
do you have anything to say?

22:23.070 --> 22:23.870
As her husband,

22:24.750 --> 22:26.460
it's my responsibility to take care of her.

22:27.260 --> 22:29.150
It must have been tough these years.

22:29.880 --> 22:30.980
No matter how hard it gets,

22:31.750 --> 22:33.270
I won't give up on her.

22:34.910 --> 22:36.090
Are you crazy?

22:36.330 --> 22:38.000
You really plan to take care of her for life?

22:38.710 --> 22:39.420
Son,

22:39.700 --> 22:41.150
I know you're responsible,

22:41.190 --> 22:42.070
but you can't

22:42.070 --> 22:43.470
ruin your life too.

22:46.550 --> 22:47.700
Don't even start.

22:47.990 --> 22:49.350
The woman I'm caring for now

22:49.380 --> 22:50.870
is completely bedridden,

22:50.950 --> 22:52.330
doing everything in bed—

22:52.550 --> 22:54.650
eating, drinking, and all.

22:55.320 --> 22:57.050
There's no dignity left.

22:57.540 --> 22:58.710
If you ask me,

22:58.750 --> 23:00.140
it'd be better if she just died.

23:04.990 --> 23:05.860
Coach Zhou.

23:07.270 --> 23:08.390
What brings you here?

23:08.830 --> 23:10.750
I just missed you.

23:31.650 --> 23:32.390
The caregiver told me

23:32.390 --> 23:33.350
you're not eating again.

23:33.990 --> 23:35.150
What do you want?

23:52.970 --> 23:54.530
I've been taking care of you for ten years.

23:56.790 --> 23:58.010
A full ten years.

24:00.850 --> 24:01.880
I've never complained.

24:01.880 --> 24:02.910
I've never said a word

24:02.950 --> 24:03.950
of resentment.

24:07.240 --> 24:09.570
I indulged myself just once,

24:13.730 --> 24:16.170
and even that's not allowed?

24:16.200 --> 24:17.230
I'm a human being!

24:17.260 --> 24:18.710
I'm a human being!

24:22.750 --> 24:24.300
You'd better start eating,

24:26.800 --> 24:28.230
or I'll get the doctor

24:28.230 --> 24:29.230
to hook you up to glucose.

24:32.540 --> 24:33.580
I won't let you die.

24:55.150 --> 24:55.630
Hello?

24:56.390 --> 24:57.080
Captain Jiang,

24:57.350 --> 24:58.640
we've looked into

24:58.670 --> 24:59.770
Zhou Zhicheng's financial records.

24:59.910 --> 25:01.150
As you suspected,

25:01.170 --> 25:02.270
there's indeed an issue.

25:02.400 --> 25:03.830
Aside from his regular salary

25:03.850 --> 25:05.010
and subsidies,

25:05.070 --> 25:06.330
at the beginning of each year,

25:06.360 --> 25:07.940
he deposits a large sum into his account,

25:07.960 --> 25:10.090
at least 300,000 yuan each time.

25:10.390 --> 25:11.350
He's been doing that

25:11.440 --> 25:12.520
for three years now.

25:13.480 --> 25:15.330
Can we trace the source of the money?

25:16.190 --> 25:17.280
I asked the bank,

25:17.310 --> 25:19.240
but each deposit was made in cash,

25:19.350 --> 25:21.180
so it's quite difficult to track.

25:21.950 --> 25:22.850
Alright, I understand.

25:25.070 --> 25:26.510
So,

25:26.560 --> 25:27.710
ever since Coach Zhou

25:27.750 --> 25:29.010
was diagnosed with cancer,

25:29.510 --> 25:30.980
someone's been giving him money

25:31.400 --> 25:32.310
for three years.

25:32.330 --> 25:33.490
Why would this person

25:33.590 --> 25:35.020
do that?

25:36.670 --> 25:37.750
We'll find out

25:37.750 --> 25:38.430
after we ask him later.

25:56.280 --> 25:57.040
Coach Zhou,

25:57.070 --> 25:57.790
it's so late.

25:57.790 --> 25:58.820
Why are you sitting out here?

25:59.220 --> 25:59.720
I-I

25:59.760 --> 26:01.260
just came out for some fresh air.

26:01.610 --> 26:02.960
It's so cold out here.

26:03.150 --> 26:03.960
Hurry and head back inside.

26:03.990 --> 26:04.830
Okay.

26:18.880 --> 26:19.770
Coach Zhou?

26:24.120 --> 26:25.020
Coach Zhou?

26:28.710 --> 26:29.400
Not at home?

26:29.400 --> 26:30.030
Coach Zhou?

26:42.140 --> 26:43.240
Mrs. Zhou.

26:46.250 --> 26:47.530
Mrs. Zhou.

26:48.070 --> 26:48.950
Where's Coach Zhou?

26:56.010 --> 26:57.030
Mrs. Zhou.

26:57.620 --> 26:59.590
You know why we're here.

27:00.880 --> 27:02.450
Did Coach Zhou and Deng Man…

27:16.820 --> 27:17.890
Something's there?

27:35.510 --> 27:37.160
Up, up.

27:37.430 --> 27:38.790
She's looking up.

27:39.720 --> 27:40.800
There's nothing here.

27:51.010 --> 27:54.390
[Hiroshima Mon Amour]

27:55.160 --> 27:56.460
"Hiroshima Mon Amour?"

27:58.810 --> 27:59.980
What are you two doing?

28:12.240 --> 28:13.230
Zhou Zhicheng,

28:13.900 --> 28:14.710
why do you have

28:14.750 --> 28:15.630
Deng Man's book?

28:43.270 --> 28:44.520
Someone fainted!

28:44.630 --> 28:45.070
Hey!

28:45.150 --> 28:46.270
-Hey.
-Are you okay?

28:46.350 --> 28:47.560
Are you okay?

28:48.350 --> 28:49.130
Hey!

28:49.190 --> 28:50.010
Man!

28:50.230 --> 28:51.050
Man!

28:51.470 --> 28:51.990
Man!

28:52.470 --> 28:53.310
What happened to her?

28:53.370 --> 28:55.140
She fainted.

28:55.790 --> 28:57.000
Did she skip breakfast today?

28:57.070 --> 28:58.600
Yes, we woke up late.

28:59.250 --> 29:00.160
Come on, give me a hand.

29:00.310 --> 29:00.950
Come on.

29:25.400 --> 29:26.360
Coach Zhou?

29:28.020 --> 29:28.710
You're awake.

29:29.610 --> 29:31.160
How are you feeling? Any better?

29:32.170 --> 29:33.270
I feel

29:34.230 --> 29:35.310
a bit better.

29:36.430 --> 29:37.780
Why are you here?

29:38.230 --> 29:39.510
You skipped breakfast, didn't you?

29:39.530 --> 29:40.420
Low blood sugar, right?

29:42.410 --> 29:43.920
You really need to eat breakfast.

29:43.990 --> 29:44.580
Skipping breakfast

29:44.630 --> 29:45.870
is very bad for your health.

29:48.470 --> 29:49.030
I don't know

29:49.030 --> 29:49.590
what you girls

29:49.640 --> 29:50.690
like to eat these days,

29:50.870 --> 29:51.960
so I just bought something random.

29:53.310 --> 29:54.270
If you ever feel dizzy again,

29:54.290 --> 29:55.210
just eat one.

29:56.550 --> 29:57.650
Thank you, Coach Zhou.

29:57.760 --> 29:58.390
No problem.

29:58.430 --> 29:59.270
Get some rest.

30:00.200 --> 30:00.940
She's awake.

30:01.550 --> 30:01.990
You're back.

30:02.070 --> 30:02.880
Yeah.

30:03.590 --> 30:04.750
Take good care of her.

30:04.790 --> 30:05.230
I'll be off.

30:05.230 --> 30:06.470
Okay, thank you, Coach Zhou.

30:06.630 --> 30:07.190
You're welcome.

30:07.190 --> 30:07.720
Goodbye.

30:08.190 --> 30:08.910
Man,

30:08.990 --> 30:10.550
you scared me to death.

30:10.630 --> 30:12.250
Why was Coach Zhou here?

30:12.310 --> 30:13.300
You should thank him.

30:13.430 --> 30:14.560
When you fainted,

30:14.590 --> 30:16.360
the boys in our class all freaked out.

30:16.430 --> 30:17.560
Fortunately, Coach Zhou was there.

30:17.670 --> 30:18.440
He came over

30:18.440 --> 30:19.510
and picked you up.

30:20.070 --> 30:21.390
Coach Zhou is so kind.

30:21.410 --> 30:23.070
I heard he's especially good to his wife.

30:23.100 --> 30:23.870
His wife's legs

30:23.870 --> 30:25.160
have been paralyzed for many years.

30:25.180 --> 30:27.430
Coach Zhou takes such good care of her

30:27.510 --> 30:29.080
that she's never even gotten bedsores.

30:29.160 --> 30:30.090
Oh my god.

30:30.670 --> 30:32.610
So attentive and responsible.

30:32.640 --> 30:34.170
Where can you find a man like that?

30:35.470 --> 30:35.990
Yeah.

30:36.030 --> 30:36.750
What a good man!

30:56.520 --> 30:57.350
Coach Zhou.

30:57.520 --> 30:58.320
Deng Man,

30:58.630 --> 30:59.670
I was thinking it must be you.

30:59.850 --> 31:00.560
Why are you still here?

31:00.630 --> 31:01.310
Why haven't you

31:01.330 --> 31:02.820
headed home for the holiday?

31:02.990 --> 31:03.590
I remember your family

31:03.590 --> 31:04.390
isn't local, right?

31:05.190 --> 31:07.660
I have nowhere to go.

31:07.910 --> 31:08.990
What do you mean?

31:08.990 --> 31:09.590
What about your parents?

31:11.190 --> 31:12.150
My parents passed away.

31:15.590 --> 31:16.110
Then,

31:16.130 --> 31:18.110
do you have any other relatives?

31:25.420 --> 31:26.550
If you don't mind,

31:26.580 --> 31:27.900
you can come to my place today.

31:28.290 --> 31:29.880
I plan to make dumplings.

31:30.750 --> 31:32.270
Wouldn't that be too much trouble for you?

31:32.270 --> 31:32.870
Not at all.

31:32.950 --> 31:33.630
At home, it's just me

31:33.630 --> 31:34.730
and my wife.

31:34.770 --> 31:36.670
Our parents don't live with us,

31:36.790 --> 31:37.890
and we don't have kids.

31:38.590 --> 31:39.150
If you come over,

31:39.190 --> 31:40.110
you can liven things up a bit.

31:41.310 --> 31:43.150
Thank you, Coach Zhou.

31:43.270 --> 31:44.170
It's nothing.

31:44.270 --> 31:45.070
Grab your things.

31:45.110 --> 31:46.140
I'll wait for you at the door.

31:52.310 --> 31:52.790
Brother,

31:53.350 --> 31:54.900
I'm almost 30,

31:55.270 --> 31:56.140
but I don't have a job

31:56.510 --> 31:57.580
or a partner.

31:57.870 --> 31:58.830
Sometimes, when I think about it,

31:58.950 --> 32:00.450
I feel really disappointed.

32:00.590 --> 32:02.140
You need to comfort her.

32:04.030 --> 32:04.960
Ling,

32:05.750 --> 32:06.710
don't be

32:06.830 --> 32:07.920
so pessimistic.

32:08.040 --> 32:09.560
You need to look ahead.

32:09.660 --> 32:13.060
♫Charging into the world, with you in my backseat♫

32:14.670 --> 32:18.020
♫Pretending not to care even though you're all I care about♫

32:19.860 --> 32:23.280
♫I couldn't tell you for some unknown reason♫

32:20.880 --> 32:21.810
Lie down for a bit.

32:22.910 --> 32:23.830
I'll go make dumplings.

32:24.030 --> 32:25.110
We're having dumplings tonight.

32:24.460 --> 32:29.520
♫That I like you the way you are♫

32:25.790 --> 32:26.150
Alright.

32:29.180 --> 32:29.830
Sorry

32:29.870 --> 32:30.430
to keep you waiting.

32:30.340 --> 32:34.710
♫Like raindrops falling, wishing to return to the sky♫

32:30.870 --> 32:32.080
Not at all, Coach Zhou.

32:32.110 --> 32:32.630
Hungry?

32:33.030 --> 32:33.470
No.

32:33.510 --> 32:34.390
I'll go make the dumplings.

32:34.950 --> 32:35.910
Let me help you.

32:35.500 --> 32:39.910
♫As long as I can meet you, I'd gladly endure anything♫

32:40.430 --> 32:44.960
♫Like a shadow quietly guarding its light source♫

32:43.510 --> 32:44.310
I'll take a look at the water.

32:45.680 --> 32:49.940
♫You keep walking, and I'll walk with you forever♫

32:49.030 --> 32:49.550
It's boiling.

32:49.550 --> 32:50.510
We'll put some in the pot in a bit.

32:50.660 --> 32:52.220
Can't you just sit there?

32:51.050 --> 32:55.760
♫You're the shooting star I chase with all my might♫

32:53.470 --> 32:54.350
You have a seat.

32:57.000 --> 33:01.430
♫I can't hold you, but I can still make a wish♫

33:02.000 --> 33:06.030
♫So precious, so bittersweet♫

33:07.810 --> 33:11.860
♫Even the wind knows the one I love is you♫

33:12.550 --> 33:16.580
♫You are the shooting star I gaze at and chase♫

33:13.790 --> 33:18.820
[Spare no effort today, ensure perfection tomorrow.]

33:18.490 --> 33:22.690
♫You saved my lonely heart♫

33:23.600 --> 33:27.520
♫I'm so lucky to have fallen for you♫

33:28.770 --> 33:32.170
♫I wish, at the edge of my world♫

33:31.210 --> 33:36.800
[Spare no effort today, ensure perfection tomorrow.]

33:31.310 --> 33:32.070
Coach Zhou.

33:33.950 --> 33:37.510
♫You'd fall in love with me too♫

33:35.870 --> 33:36.940
I'm here to return the candy.

33:40.390 --> 33:41.240
You can keep it.

33:44.550 --> 33:45.490
I'm leaving.

33:58.790 --> 34:02.860
♫The streetlight watches you leave♫

34:02.960 --> 34:03.800
Why are you here?

34:04.320 --> 34:08.350
♫These hands can't yet hold onto love♫

34:07.550 --> 34:09.230
I came to look for something.

34:09.659 --> 34:12.960
♫I don't want to miss any of your tearful or joyful moments♫

34:11.550 --> 34:12.270
Go ahead.

34:12.350 --> 34:13.360
I'm taking inventory.

34:14.620 --> 34:18.830
♫That I like you the way you are♫

34:19.550 --> 34:23.960
♫Like raindrops falling, wishing to return to the sky♫

34:25.070 --> 34:29.060
♫As long as I can meet you, I'd gladly endure anything♫

34:30.179 --> 34:34.190
♫Like a shadow quietly guarding its light source♫

34:34.969 --> 34:39.030
♫You keep walking, and I'll walk with you forever♫

34:36.510 --> 34:37.590
What are you looking for?

34:37.679 --> 34:38.630
I'll help you find it.

34:39.750 --> 34:41.360
Actually, I came to find you.

34:40.340 --> 34:44.920
♫You're the shooting star I chase with all my might♫

34:44.880 --> 34:46.500
You don't have to keep coming to me.

34:45.900 --> 34:50.560
♫I can't hold you, but I can still make a wish♫

34:46.710 --> 34:47.429
You're young.

34:47.510 --> 34:48.389
Get out more.

34:48.440 --> 34:49.310
Hang out with your peers.

34:49.389 --> 34:50.270
Date someone.

34:51.429 --> 34:52.750
I don't want to date.

34:51.570 --> 34:55.590
♫So precious, so bittersweet♫

34:53.199 --> 34:54.250
That's fine too.

34:54.630 --> 34:55.510
Focus on your studies.

34:56.070 --> 34:57.390
After you start working,

34:56.600 --> 35:00.770
♫Please let me know I'm in your heart too♫

34:58.070 --> 34:59.230
you'll meet plenty of outstanding young men.

35:02.080 --> 35:05.800
♫You are the shooting star I gaze at and chase♫

35:03.360 --> 35:04.200
Coach Zhou.

35:06.620 --> 35:10.860
♫You saved my lonely heart♫

35:06.830 --> 35:08.110
There's someone I like.

35:12.250 --> 35:16.460
♫I'm so lucky to have fallen for you♫

35:15.990 --> 35:16.630
Deng Man.

35:17.720 --> 35:18.510
Actually, I...

35:17.830 --> 35:20.980
♫I wish, at the edge of my world♫

35:18.550 --> 35:21.170
You'll understand after you read this.

35:20.050 --> 35:22.430
[Hiroshima Mon Amour]

35:22.140 --> 35:26.400
♫You'd fall in love with me too♫

35:29.050 --> 35:30.990
[Hiroshima Mon Amour]

36:05.240 --> 36:06.090
Deng Man,

36:06.170 --> 36:07.080
you keep coming here,

36:07.110 --> 36:08.230
and it's affecting our training.

36:08.970 --> 36:10.710
Don't come again.

36:12.220 --> 36:13.510
I understand,

36:13.930 --> 36:16.350
but you keep avoiding me.

36:17.520 --> 36:18.920
You're too young.

36:19.130 --> 36:19.870
You don't even know

36:19.870 --> 36:20.870
what you're doing.

36:23.420 --> 36:24.440
I'm sorry.

36:25.470 --> 36:27.340
Anyway, I've said what I need to.

36:28.300 --> 36:29.580
Please don't come again.

36:35.990 --> 36:37.200
Put them back in.

36:39.710 --> 36:40.350
Okay.

36:42.760 --> 36:43.890
Clean up properly.

36:45.520 --> 36:46.240
Okay.

37:09.910 --> 37:11.230
Why didn't you fight back?

37:13.830 --> 37:14.930
I don't mind.

37:18.190 --> 37:19.070
Don't you know that by doing this,

37:19.090 --> 37:20.600
you'll only encourage them to go further?

37:21.540 --> 37:23.250
Are you worried about me?

37:38.480 --> 37:39.430
Coach Zhou.

37:40.470 --> 37:42.260
I know this is wrong,

37:42.860 --> 37:44.800
but I can't help it.

37:44.980 --> 37:46.960
I really like you.

37:47.680 --> 37:49.510
I know you have a family,

37:51.020 --> 37:52.500
and I don't want to interfere.

37:52.500 --> 37:53.580
I just want

37:54.320 --> 37:55.890
to watch you from afar.

37:55.910 --> 37:56.870
Enough, Deng Man.

37:57.190 --> 37:58.430
Stop. This isn't right.

38:00.270 --> 38:01.910
Wait, wait, wait.

38:01.970 --> 38:04.000
Don't leave me, Coach Zhou.

38:04.220 --> 38:05.380
Please,

38:05.460 --> 38:06.900
just stay a little longer.

38:07.550 --> 38:08.360
Maybe ten minutes?

38:09.010 --> 38:09.820
Or

38:10.150 --> 38:11.490
three minutes will be enough.

38:16.490 --> 38:17.130
Deng Man.

38:20.190 --> 38:21.190
You're so young.

38:23.270 --> 38:24.110
I'm afraid you've misunderstood

38:24.110 --> 38:25.030
your feelings.

38:26.640 --> 38:28.840
I'm very sure about my feelings for you.

38:29.710 --> 38:30.910
And I feel for you too.

38:31.950 --> 38:32.790
You've been carrying such

38:32.870 --> 38:34.070
a heavy burden

38:34.070 --> 38:35.330
for so many years

38:35.740 --> 38:36.890
while others call you

38:37.390 --> 38:38.350
responsible

38:38.430 --> 38:39.750
and a good man.

38:41.910 --> 38:43.170
But no one

38:43.440 --> 38:45.050
sees your pain.
